<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>About Me</title>
    <style>
      body {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        font-family: 'Verdana', sans-serif;
        background: #f5f5f5;
        color: #333;
      }

      .container {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        max-width: 1000px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 2rem;
        align-items: center;
        background: #fff;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        border-radius: 10px;
      }

      .photo {
        flex: .2 1 200px;
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
      }

      .photo img {
        max-width: 100%;
        height: auto;
        border-radius: 10px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }

      .text {
        flex: 2 1 500px;
        padding: 1rem;
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        color: #333;
      }

      p {
        line-height: 1.6;
        font-size: 1.1rem;
      }

      @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .container {
          flex-direction: column;
          text-align: center;
        }

        .text {
          padding: 0;
        }

        .photo {
          margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="photo">
        <img src="profile2.jpg" alt="Leo Hoerdemann" />
      </div>
      <div class="text">
        <h1>About Me</h1>
        <p>
          Hello, my name is Leo Hoerdemann.  
          I am a recent graduate from Michigan State University 
          with a degree in Computer Science with minors in Computational Math and Business. 
          I have worked mostly with game development, data science, and webserver development. 
          I have experience with languages such as C#, Python, C++, JS, Java, and a few others. 
          I've used technology for both frameworks and  engines, to development cycles, and many other tools. 
          I'm also experienced with audio technologies such as Ableton and wwise in my free time. 
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
